{"tid":91943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見男朋友家長有咩要注意","createTime":"2017-01-23T08:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T10:52:15.000Z","uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02acb1cde29225fcdc3b810ed2422d941895f8c8","tid":91943,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"終於話帶我返去見家長了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次見家長 唔識要點做<br />\n兩個都係大學生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知引唔引到隔離post個巴打留低高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5caf143466cd0c8fdb9fb3b946258db209514592","tid":91943,"uid":21088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T08:04:49.000Z","msg":"做返自己"},{"pid":"d74da3dbd616bb90235d879dbff673b3108c8870","tid":91943,"uid":51308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T08:08:03.000Z","msg":"我自己就覺得唔洗刻意話買好多野上去<br />\n<br />\n都係食餐飯就買d啤酒 汽水 <br />\n<br />\n同埋表現得大方得體d 唔好痴實個男朋友同太親熱<br />\n<br />\n又唔係叫你又幫手洗碗又盛 主人家都唔會比你做<br />\n<br />\n但開飯幫手鋪下檯 上下菜 分下筷子你做到加嘛<br />\n<br />\n自己執生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fc0277601c953fa3ac2a74e3ba40985dd68c44","tid":91943,"uid":1386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T08:09:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a79d580d55115ebedd657db659df81cf1439daff","tid":91943,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T08:10:10.000Z","msg":"著低胸短裙黑絲"},{"pid":"4faf0aeb21a42a50c518a623c97d07e536a8e57d","tid":91943,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T08:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做返自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但禮儀上可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪唔好著短裙<br />\n著高跟鞋係咪唔係咁好<br />\n係咪唔應該化妝<br />\n<br />\n男朋友叫唔洗買禮物<br />\n但我覺得一定要<br />\n記得男朋友話佢爸爸中意飲茶 <br />\n所以我有諗過去天仁茗茶買盒茶 <br />\n但咁樣係咪要買埋禮物比其他屋企人？<br />\n定係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006e69c2c59a8332791e541a889fb0a4f7d1ecd2","tid":91943,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T08:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己就覺得唔洗刻意話買好多野上去<br />\n<br />\n都係食餐飯就買d啤酒 汽水 <br />\n<br />\n同埋表現得大方得體d 唔好痴實個男朋友同太親熱<br />\n<br />\n又唔係叫你又幫手洗碗又盛 主人家都唔會比你做<br />\n<br />\n但開飯幫手鋪下檯 上下菜 分下筷子你做到加嘛<br />\n<br />\n自己執生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係拖下手都唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁如果唔喺屋企食 出去食咁點"},{"pid":"afc5f673fdaba694e399bfae6a2f9377f594356c","tid":91943,"uid":78001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T08:56:12.000Z","msg":"着衫方面唔好太過open 老一輩既人都比較保守 第一印象好重要 一兩次熟佐後就可以唔洗太過著重衣着 但有一點好重要 就係食飯前一定要識得叫人食飯 或者禮貌上都要問句洗唔洗幫手（拎筷子嗰d）"},{"pid":"bca2b291985a58e2747a8a424dec6c098e807fd4","tid":91943,"uid":69486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"認真，切記要幫手洗碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扮下野都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都要入下廚房幫手<br />\n<br />\n阿媽會覺得咁樣識幫下手做家務係好女仔嘅表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e6d49ef9f3ad5311024f88662ad236e4bd0404","tid":91943,"uid":59059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:00:09.000Z","msg":"淡妝<br />\n當然唔好性感衣著啦<br />\n<br />\n樓上講得好，食完飯幫手洗碗加分！<br />\n其他野就自自然然啦"},{"pid":"2fa10ce33744a3e6e75307f30ffeb075db868106","tid":91943,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:52:15.000Z","msg":"買雞精做禮物會唔會太旱<br />\n因為佢妹妹就考試"}]}